
`.gitignore`
```gitignore
# Environment / secrets
.env
config/.env
config/*.local
systemd/meeting-capture.service
systemd/meeting-postprocess.service
systemd/meeting-postprocess.path
*.secret
*.token

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/

# Logs
*.log

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/

# Runtime outputs
meeting-recordings/
meeting-transcripts/
meeting-summaries/
tmp/
cache/

# Audio / transcript artifacts
*.wav
*.mp3
*.m4a
*.flac
*.srt
*.vtt
